import os

def scanfile(path, res, k):
    filelist = os.listdir(path)
    for filename in filelist:
        filepath = os.path.join(path,filename)
        if os.path.isdir(filepath):
            scanfile(filepath, res, k)
        elif k in filepath:
            res.append(filepath)
    return res

from math import *
In [36]:
def distance(lat1, lon1, lat2, lon2):
    lat1, lon1, lat2, lon2 = map(radians, [float(lat1), float(lon1), float(lat2), float(lon2)])
    dlon = lon2-lon1
    dlat = lat2-lat1
    a = sin(dlat/2)**2 + cos(lat1) * cos(lat2) * sin(dlon/2)**2
    c = 2 * asin(sqrt(a))
    r = 6378
    
    return c*r

travel_min_to_CBD = []
for i in tqdm(data.train_station_id):
    t_ = []
    for j in train_lis:
        train = stop_time[stop_time.trip_id==j]
        if i in train.stop_id.to_list() and 20043 in train.stop_id.to_list():
            t1 = train[train["stop_id"]==i]["departure_time"]
            t2 = train[train["stop_id"]==20043]["arrival_time"]
            if t2.values[0]>t1.values[0]:
                t_diff = pd.to_datetime(t2.values[0])-pd.to_datetime(t1.values[0])
                t_.append(t_diff.seconds/60)
            else:
                continue
        elif i in train.stop_id.to_list() and 22180 in train.stop_id.to_list():
            t1 = train[train["stop_id"]==i]["departure_time"]
            t2 = train[train["stop_id"]==22180]["arrival_time"]
            if t2.values[0]>t1.values[0]:
                t_diff = pd.to_datetime(t2.values[0])-pd.to_datetime(t1.values[0])
                t_.append(t_diff.seconds/60)
            else:
                continue
        else:
            continue
    if t_:
        travel_min_to_CBD.append(np.mean(t_))
    else:
        travel_min_to_CBD.append(0)

In [119]:
Y = pd.to_datetime(data["Date"]).dt.year
for inx, suburb in enumerate(data.Suburb):
    year = Y[inx]
    for j in council_dic.keys():
        if suburb.upper() in j.replace("'", "").replace('[', '').replace(']', '').split(', '):
            df = crime[crime["Local Government Area"] == council_dic[j]]
            df = df[(df["Apr - Mar reference period"]<year) & (df["Apr - Mar reference period"]>=year-3)]
            a = df.groupby('crime_type').mean()[["Offence Count"]].loc['A', "Offence Count"]
            b = df.groupby('crime_type').mean()[["Offence Count"]].loc['B', "Offence Count"]
            c = df.groupby('crime_type').mean()[["Offence Count"]].loc['C', "Offence Count"]
            data.loc[inx, "crime_A_average"] = a
            data.loc[inx, "crime_B_average"] = b
            data.loc[inx, "crime_C_average"] = c

def log_transform(df=ppc_data):
    for col in df.columns:
        df[col] = df[col].apply(lambda x: np.log(x))
    return df
